<h3></h3>
<h3>Helping a Friend or Loved One</h3>
<p>It takes a lot of courage to refer a friend or loved one for counseling. Follow the appropriate path below to find out exactly how you can help your friend or loved one.</p>
<h3></h3>
<h3>Confidentiality Notice</h3>
<p>Anything a student discusses with a counselor is held in strict confidence. We will not release any information to you unless a <a href="Documents/counseling-center/ROI 06-2012.pdf" target="_blank">Release of Information </a>is signed. This includes if a student is being seen in our office or if they have kept their appointment. We ask that you speak directly with the student to learn this information and/or request to have them sign the appropriate form.</p>
